      At the moment I'm located in Colorado, though I’m an avid traveler and have spent many moons doing the "digital
      nomad" thing. I also love motorcycles, yoga, and reading. If you’re nosy like me, or curious to hear more, take a
      peek at <a href="/now" class="link rosegold">what I’m up to now.</a>
      <br /><br />
      I’m currently looking for my next full time role, so please peruse my sight, my resume, and
      <a href="mailto:bryn.codes@gmail.com" class="link rosegold">get in touch!</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

